    {\displaystyle \sigma _{1}^{2}=\sigma _{2}^{2}=\sigma _{3}^{2}=-i\,\sigma _{1}\sigma _{2}\sigma _{3}={\begin{pmatrix}1&0\\0&1\end{pmatrix}}=I}
  where I is the identity matrix.
The determinants and traces of the Pauli matrices are:

  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                det
                
                  σ
                  
                    j
                  
                
              
              
                 
