        (
        
          
            R
          
          
            3
          
        
        
          )
          
            ∗
          
        
         
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ {\text{Mat}}_{2\times 2}(\mathbb {C} )\otimes (\mathbb {R} ^{3})^{*}\ }
   which maps 
  
    
      
         
        
          
            
              a
              →
            
          
        
        ↦
        
          
            
              a
              →
            
          
        
        ⋅
        
          
            
              σ
              →
            
          
        
         
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ {\vec {a}}\mapsto {\vec {a}}\cdot {\vec {\sigma }}~.}

Completeness relation
Each component of 
  
    
      
         
        
          
            
              a
              →
            
          
        
         
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ {\vec {a}}\ }
   can be recovered from the matrix (see completeness relation below) 

